Package: pushme
Title: Send Push Messages When Running R Scripts
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: 
    person("Magdalena", "Bennett", , "m.bennett@austin.utexas.edu", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: "Wrapper package for `pushoverr` functions to send push notifications with random messages to your phone and/or computer when code is done or there is an error.".
